E. H. Calvert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E._H._Calvert 0 Elisha Helm Calvert (June 27, 1863 – October 5, 1941) was an American film actor and director. He appeared in more than 170 films, as well as directing a further 60 titles. Elisha_Helm_Calvert ( June_27_,_1863 – October_5_,_1941 ) was an_American_film_actor_and_director .
